    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning collector, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains in a pristine, original state. Every mechanical component has been meticulously preserved to ensure a driving experience that is indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a benchmark-quality vehicle of the highest pedigree.",
      "price": 48900.0,
